MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2005- 0201. Gass v. Massachusetts Mut. Life Ins. Co.

Summit App. No. 21956. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Summit County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
